      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "JS\n\nBranden Eich - 1995\n\nMocha - Live Script - JavaScrpit\n\nECMA - European Computer Manifacturing Association\n\n1997 - ECMA Scrpit(ES1 v)\n\nMost popular version Es6\n\nFeatures - 1. Js is dynamically type in nature\n              2. Add Functionality\n              3. scripting lanaguage \n              4. loosely \n\nJS is an syncronise by deafult\n\nprimitive            non-primitive\n\nnumber               array\nstring                object\nboolean              function\nnull\nundefined\nbigInt\nsymbol  \n\n\nFunctions:- \n\n                    \n                    DOM Tree                                                Document node(root node)\n                                                                element node,attribute node,text node,comment node\n              \n                    Document\n           \n                      <html>\n\n        <head>                       <body>\n\n<meta>  <meta>  <meta>        <h1>     <div>\n\n\n \n\n",
