      "updated": 1776227015559,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TypeScript:\n\nIt is programming language \nIt is a superset of js\nIt is optionally statically typed\n\nFeatures of TS:\n\n1.Supports static typing\n2.type inference\n3.Supports ES6 & new features\n4.Cross browser compatitbility\n5.Detects errors at compile time\n\n\n\n\nWhy TypeScrpit over Js?\n\n1.We will get errors at compile\n2.Ts provides Type Safety\n\n\n\nHistory of TypeScript\n\nMicrosoft introduced in 2012\n\n2014 -> typeScript 1.0\n2016 -> angular used ts\n\n2026 -> TypeScript 6.02(Latest Version)\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TypeScript:\n\nIt is programming language \nIt is a superset of js\nIt is optionally statically typed\n\nFeatures of TS:\n\n1.Supports static typing\n2.type inference\n3.Supports ES6 & new features\n4.Cross browser compatitbility\n5.Detects errors at compile time\n\n\n\n\nWhy TypeScrpit over Js?\n\n1.We will get errors at compile\n2.Ts provides Type Safety\n\n\n\nHistory of TypeScript\n\nMicrosoft introduced in 2012\n\n2014 -> typeScript 1.0\n2016 -> angular used ts\n\n2026 -> TypeScript 6.02(Latest Version)\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
